d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係話唔好睇，只係覺得有啲吹大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買齊小說覺得寫得唔錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而動畫第一季麻麻,可能制作組冇諗過出到第二季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我只係唔鍾意佢次次都係扮晒野，<br />\n係咁FF 乜都驚一餐，跟住就大幅描寫佢點SM人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開始有啲悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就幾鍾意睇個種反差嘅描寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個當安茲神咁拜但佢骨子裏都只係一個普通人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過夏提雅之後都未有一個似樣嘅對手係差咁啲"},{"pid":"c627f3d94a9c6607251e4aff1e6b2cf02893cdd7","tid":151613,"uid":28042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T20:04:08.000Z","msg":"小說有冇講點解入左game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係睇過動畫"},{"pid":"6c2a5737f6253e04451ef5c1a865f7c655adc4a4","tid":151613,"uid":3768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T23:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小說有冇講點解入左game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係睇過動畫</blockquote><br />\n唔係game黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係異世界 只係仲用到個game d系統"},{"pid":"9da266bf97d00f67e7aea5bd311e36edfc24fd34","tid":151613,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T23:58:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正！ 幾時到記錄的地平線第三季</blockquote><br />\n幾時有 HL3?<br />\n幾時有 TF3?<br />\n幾時有L4D3?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n魔禁3叫緊糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係唔係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好呃我喎"},{"pid":"f03db6f099c09e5da5b18fdf0ff990909ebcba3f","tid":151613,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小說有冇講點解入左game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係睇過動畫</blockquote><br />\n唔係game黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係異世界 只係仲用到個game d系統</blockquote><br />\n其實從來都唔係GAME<br />\n隻GAME本身就係利用異世界既空間去寫出黎(類似鏡世界)<br />\n所以世界法則同故事入面既異世界好自然會相近<br />\n隻GAME係負責將你既精神連接落去你異世界既身體(角色)<br />\n熄SERVER時GAME世界被破壞,某D人既精神同異世界身體依然連接既關係<br />\n導致GAME世界既設定套用左落去故事入面既異世界<br />\n而點解D人會出現於唔同時間線上,係基於數據量<br />\n大墓地既數據太大導致傳送時間落後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">申利:鳩UP</span></span>"},{"pid":"348bca0b5080f8d8e373e3dba9d3ad5e9ebc4082","tid":151613,"uid":34602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:56:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買齊小說既我覺得中左伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過份吹捧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中伏位係咩先</blockquote><br />\n一路去到而家都係主角成日FF有強敵，<br />\n之後就剩係講主角群有幾屈機，不斷秒殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係話唔好睇，只係覺得有啲吹大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買齊小說覺得寫得唔錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而動畫第一季麻麻,可能制作組冇諗過出到第二季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我只係唔鍾意佢次次都係扮晒野，<br />\n係咁FF 乜都驚一餐，跟住就大幅描寫佢點SM人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開始有啲悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以唔係佢做主角果時先好睇，班異世界人每次打交都係用條命打...有血有肉好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1efd1521d71de5e6468bdcc8f3f756d1550fb7","tid":151613,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾時先肯做史萊姆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有生之年有既</blockquote><br />\n做咩咁灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩阻滯"},{"pid":"d257b01338caf47cfa0f5d2123ef5d8da0dd01ae","tid":151613,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買齊小說既我覺得中左伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過份吹捧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中伏位係咩先</blockquote><br />\n一路去到而家都係主角成日FF有強敵，<br />\n之後就剩係講主角群有幾屈機，不斷秒殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係話唔好睇，只係覺得有啲吹大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買齊小說覺得寫得唔錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而動畫第一季麻麻,可能制作組冇諗過出到第二季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我只係唔鍾意佢次次都係扮晒野，<br />\n係咁FF 乜都驚一餐，跟住就大幅描寫佢點SM人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開始有啲悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就幾鍾意睇個種反差嘅描寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個當安茲神咁拜但佢骨子裏都只係一個普通人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過夏提雅之後都未有一個似樣嘅對手係差咁啲</blockquote><br />\n呢個就係我覺得悶既地方，夏提雅之後，<br />\n去到第8定9 卷都冇似樣既戰鬥，<br />\n一路都係講主角班人扮傻，對面睇唔起，之後弱殺，<br />\n當然你可以話本野重點唔係呢度，<br />\n但我諗好多人同我一樣會諗住有D高水平既大戰睇，先會買書，<br />\n而我都唔係話唔好睇，只係話吹大左，俾我選多一次我唔會買書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本野仲要鬼死咁厚特別貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf1b5f4050794e6e2dc3118c404f543500f85a0","tid":151613,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買齊小說既我覺得中左伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過份吹捧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中伏位係咩先</blockquote><br />\n一路去到而家都係主角成日FF有強敵，<br />\n之後就剩係講主角群有幾屈機，不斷秒殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係話唔好睇，只係覺得有啲吹大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買齊小說覺得寫得唔錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而動畫第一季麻麻,可能制作組冇諗過出到第二季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我只係唔鍾意佢次次都係扮晒野，<br />\n係咁FF 乜都驚一餐，跟住就大幅描寫佢點SM人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開始有啲悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就幾鍾意睇個種反差嘅描寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個當安茲神咁拜但佢骨子裏都只係一個普通人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過夏提雅之後都未有一個似樣嘅對手係差咁啲</blockquote><br />\n呢個就係我覺得悶既地方，夏提雅之後，<br />\n去到第8定9 卷都冇似樣既戰鬥，<br />\n一路都係講主角班人扮傻，對面睇唔起，之後弱殺，<br />\n當然你可以話本野重點唔係呢度，<br />\n但我諗好多人同我一樣會諗住有D高水平既大戰睇，先會買書，<br />\n而我都唔係話唔好睇，只係話吹大左，俾我選多一次我唔會買書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本野仲要鬼死咁厚特別貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全個世界最勁就係佢地<br />\n是但一個都係移動災難<br />\n唯一做到佢地都係留落既道具<br />\n好難再有高汁對戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9baf4026b58e2a7e520d1002c743d87773a21944","tid":151613,"uid":34602